{"tw": {"3633750": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "冒險途中全員告白", "steam_appid": 3633750, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >離鄉背井終於到達目的地，卻在當天就被告知地城已被踏破？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >慶祝的漫天彩花飛舞、歌舞美酒齊出。原本想蹭上「攻略地城」名號，好跟家裡證明實力的我，卻在抵達的當天就看到別的小隊完成攻略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出於無奈只好轉移陣地的我，只好先挑了個附近的小村莊「梅多村」打聽是否可能會有新生地城的消息，卻因為被村長知道出生於盛產壯陽魔獸的格雷夫，打著協助推銷與打響名號的建議，莫名其妙被拜託提升梅多村的存在感（？）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在村子生活的過程中，不管是善於賣弄可愛的公會櫃台小姐、還是看似樸素但深藏不露的道具店女兒、又或是單純熱情卻是武器癡的武器店妹妹、溫柔婉約的單親酒館老闆娘、一不注意就想對我下手的魔法店主人，都在不知不覺之間跟她們越走越近了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/a7d2df68d3dccb9e36a74faaf54a8ca7.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/a7d2df68d3dccb9e36a74faaf54a8ca7.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/a7d2df68d3dccb9e36a74faaf54a8ca7.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嗯……或許在這裡停留的時間會比預想的還要長一點呢。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲方式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b7b9229597985f306498c0318f13f990.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b7b9229597985f306498c0318f13f990.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b7b9229597985f306498c0318f13f990.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/1f39f091c196137e9cd53942e26e33cb.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/4abb3a0329a4ce6c65182c981c175c21.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/4abb3a0329a4ce6c65182c981c175c21.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/4abb3a0329a4ce6c65182c981c175c21.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >輕鬆採集、提升等級、達成委託、提升村莊知名度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接下每間商店或是公會的委託並且達成回報，前往新的地方開啟更多的故事與劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這些忙碌的日常中，逐漸累積村子名氣，以及各種商店的五位女角好感度吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是在店裡、還是村莊或郊外，在這些點點滴滴生活發生的有趣、溫馨、或是意外事件中，一起締造各種屬於你們之間的回憶♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇精美作畫全動態H場景</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇學習各種技能，將它們運用在採集、日常，或瑟瑟上</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇多達五位不同性格的女性角色可供攻略（或者說被攻略？）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇培養每個人的好感，觸發特殊劇情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇女主角全日文配音</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆女角簡介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇道具店店員：翠西</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >害羞內向卻是村裡的活百科，樸素的外表下，似乎藏著不為人知的嗜好……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/fef7a719b814bdd0b3aa85705b6d6a78.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇武器店學徒：伊萊</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >單純直率，提到武器就兩眼發光。除了武器以外的都顯得有些無知…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/ed9657d7680c4bd2bac9c29a8b75555a.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇魔法店店長：茉伊拉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與村裡人格格不入的海族女子，初見便惡作劇似地捉弄你。但這或許不只是無聊的舉動……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/5c0088783562995a539860b169d1c080.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇酒館老闆娘：莎柏琳娜</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >獨自帶著女兒經營酒館，總是親切待人。然而溫暖笑容下，偶爾流露出的寂寞令人在意……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/80a5502a4a70b8d796e62723f087c402.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇公會櫃台：桃樂絲</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甜言蜜語與可愛是她的武器，總能讓冒險者言聽計從。但這背後或許藏著另一層意圖……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c73527c9950da912e9d5557b93a34845.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆故事背景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >離鄉背井終於到達目的地，卻在當天就被告知地城已被踏破？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >慶祝的漫天彩花飛舞、歌舞美酒齊出。原本想蹭上「攻略地城」名號，好跟家裡證明實力的我，卻在抵達的當天就看到別的小隊完成攻略。</p><p clas