"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/4abb3a0329a4ce6c65182c981c175c21.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/4abb3a0329a4ce6c65182c981c175c21.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/4abb3a0329a4ce6c65182c981c175c21.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >輕鬆採集、提升等級、達成委託、提升村莊知名度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接下每間商店或是公會的委託並且達成回報，前往新的地方開啟更多的故事與劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這些忙碌的日常中，逐漸累積村子名氣，以及各種商店的五位女角好感度吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不管是在店裡、還是村莊或郊外，在這些點點滴滴生活發生的有趣、溫馨、或是意外事件中，一起締造各種屬於你們之間的回憶♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆遊戲特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.s