ass=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/ed9657d7680c4bd2bac9c29a8b75555a.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇魔法店店長：茉伊拉</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與村裡人格格不入的海族女子，初見便惡作劇似地捉弄你。但這或許不只是無聊的舉動……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/5c0088783562995a539860b169d1c080.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇酒館老闆娘：莎柏琳娜</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >獨自帶著女兒經營酒館，總是親切待人。然而溫暖笑容下，偶爾流露出的寂寞令人在意……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/80a5502a4a70b8d796e62723f087c402.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇公會櫃台：桃樂絲</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >甜言蜜語與可愛是她的武器，總能讓冒險者言聽計從。但這背後或許藏著另一層意圖……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c73527c9950da912e9d5557b93a34845.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p>", "short_description": "充滿鬥志想要挑戰，卻在抵達當天地城就被人踏破！？ 為了尋找新地城的線索而來到這座村莊，卻突然被拜託幫忙村莊度過危機，開啟了瘋狂幫村中商店收集素材的任務。 道具店的樸素村娘，武器店的爽朗元氣女孩，魔法舖的神祕異族女子，酒館的爆乳老闆娘，冒險者公會的可愛活潑小姐，我怎麼突然就跟這些人擦出火花了？！究竟我的冒險者人生會變成怎樣呢！", "supported_languages": "繁體中文, 英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 韓文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/ab0f12fd2370fc749880680a8c47ded536f22e98/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1774379683", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/e52123d11afa0d0c19285332eb2380f3f6c9b0d1/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1774379683", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/e52123d11afa0d0c19285332eb2380f3f6c9b0d1/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1774379683", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 560 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4.3 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 760 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 4.3 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026"}}}}, "us": {"3633750": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Love Confessions on the Adventure", "steam_appid": 3633750, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Story Background</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After leaving home and finally reaching my destination, I was told the dungeon had already been conquered on the very same day?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fireworks lit up the sky in celebration, with singing, dancing, and wine flowing freely. I had hoped to ride the fame of &quot;conquering the dungeon&quot; to prove my worth to my family, only to witness another party complete the mission on the day I arrived.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With no other choice, I shifted my focus and headed to a nearby village called Meadow Village to gather news of any newly discovered dungeons. But upon learning that I was born in Grave, a region known for its virility boosting magical beasts, the village chief under the guise of helping me promote my name roped me into raising the village’s visibility (somehow?!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While living in the village, I found myself growing unexpectedly close to the women around me: the charmingly manipulative guild receptionist, the shy but mysterious daughter of the item shop, the weapon obsessed blacksmith apprentice, the gentle and graceful single mother tavern owner, and the unpredictable magic shop owner who keeps trying to make a move on me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/6b417ba0e545a6881cc32b3a2329c02f.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/6b417ba0e545a6881cc32b3a2329c02f.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/6b417ba0e545a6881cc32b3a2329c02f.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hmm… Maybe I’ll end up staying here longer than I thought.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/eaad9c01f5ff05cbeff04f9985f1f8e9.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/eaad9c01f5ff05cbeff04f9985f1f8e9.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/eaad9c01f5ff05cbeff04f9985f1f8e9.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/2c8f2efac396d7e8441ca418861370ea.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/37682df59dc0442c3e29e15fe43233ea.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/37682df59dc0442c3e29e15fe43233ea.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/37682df59dc0442c3e29e15fe43233ea.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials, level up, complete requests, and raise the village’s fame all at your own pace!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on requests from each shop or the guild and report back once completed. Unlock new stories and events as you explore different areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you go about your busy daily life, you'll gradually build the village’s reputation and deepen your bonds with the five heroines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're in the shops, village, or outskirts, create lasting memories through fun, heartwarming, or unexpected events in your shared life together ♥.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇ Fully animated H-scenes with beautiful artwork</strong><br><strong> ◇ Learn various skills and use them for gathering, daily life... or lewd activities</strong><br><strong> ◇ Five heroines with unique personalities to pursue (or be pursued by?)</strong><br><strong> ◇ Raise their affection to unlock special story events</strong><br><strong> ◇ Full Japanese voice acting for all heroines</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Character Profiles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Tracy – Item Shop Assistant</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shy and introverted, but a walking encyclopedia of the village. Beneath her modest appearance hides a secret hobby…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/fef7a719b814bdd0b3aa85705b6d6a78.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Eli – Blacksmith Apprentice</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple and honest, her eyes light up at the mention of weapons. Beyond that, she's a bit clueless…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/ed9657d7680c4bd2bac9c29a8b75555a.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Moira – Magic Shop Owner</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A sea dwelling outsider with a mischievous streak. From your very first meeting, she plays tricks on you but maybe there’s more behind it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/5c0088783562995a539860b169d1c080.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Sabrina – Tavern Owner</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A gentle and elegant single mother running the tavern on her own. Always kind, but her warm smile sometimes reveals a hint of loneliness…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/80a5502a4a70b8d796e62723f087c402.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Dorothy – Guild Receptionist</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > She charms adventurers with sweet words and cuteness, always getting them to do her bidding. But could there be a hidden agenda behind that smile…?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c73527c9950da912e9d5557b93a34845.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Story Background</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After leaving home and finally reaching my destination, I was told the dungeon had already been conquered on the very same day?!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fireworks lit up the sky in celebration, with singing, dancing, and wine flowing freely. I had hoped to ride the fame of &quot;conquering the dungeon&quot; to prove my worth to my family, only to witness another party complete the mission on the day I arrived.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With no other choice, I shifted my focus and headed to a nearby village called Meadow Village to gather news of any newly discovered dungeons. But upon learning that I was born in Grave, a region known for its virility boosting magical beasts, the village chief under the guise of helping me promote my name roped me into raising the village’s visibility (somehow?!).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While living in the village, I found myself growing unexpectedly close to the women around me: the charmingly manipulative guild receptionist, the shy but mysterious daughter of the item shop, the weapon obsessed blacksmith apprentice, the gentle and graceful single mother tavern owner, and the unpredictable magic shop owner who keeps trying to make a move on me.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/6b417ba0e545a6881cc32b3a2329c02f.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/6b417ba0e545a6881cc32b3a2329c02f.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/6b417ba0e545a6881cc32b3a2329c02f.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hmm… Maybe I’ll end up staying here longer than I thought.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/eaad9c01f5ff05cbeff04f9985f1f8e9.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/eaad9c01f5ff05cbeff04f9985f1f8e9.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/eaad9c01f5ff05cbeff04f9985f1f8e9.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/2c8f2efac396d7e8441ca418861370ea.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/37682df59dc0442c3e29e15fe43233ea.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/37682df59dc0442c3e29e15fe43233ea.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/37682df59dc0442c3e29e15fe43233ea.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gather materials, level up, complete requests, and raise the village’s fame all at your own pace!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on requests from each shop or the guild and report back once completed. Unlock new stories and events as you explore different areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you go about your busy daily life, you'll gradually build the village’s reputation and deepen your bonds with the five heroines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're in the shops, village, or outskirts, create lasting memories through fun, heartwarming, or unexpected events in your shared life together ♥.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b1c4368ff5419e7197fb8454567df6d0.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=1080 height=608 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c6bd6f16ef8d35ae93bfa3d9c0c86523.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.poster.avif?t=1774379683\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.webm?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/b2832ce493405c45cebdac0068eb4b45.mp4?t=1774379683\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>◇ Fully animated H-scenes with beautiful artwork</strong><br><strong> ◇ Learn various skills and use them for gathering, daily life... or lewd activities</strong><br><strong> ◇ Five heroines with unique personalities to pursue (or be pursued by?)</strong><br><strong> ◇ Raise their affection to unlock special story events</strong><br><strong> ◇ Full Japanese voice acting for all heroines</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆Character Profiles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Tracy – Item Shop Assistant</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Shy and introverted, but a walking encyclopedia of the village. Beneath her modest appearance hides a secret hobby…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/fef7a719b814bdd0b3aa85705b6d6a78.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Eli – Blacksmith Apprentice</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple and honest, her eyes light up at the mention of weapons. Beyond that, she's a bit clueless…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/ed9657d7680c4bd2bac9c29a8b75555a.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Moira – Magic Shop Owner</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A sea dwelling outsider with a mischievous streak. From your very first meeting, she plays tricks on you but maybe there’s more behind it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/5c0088783562995a539860b169d1c080.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Sabrina – Tavern Owner</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A gentle and elegant single mother running the tavern on her own. Always kind, but her warm smile sometimes reveals a hint of loneliness…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/80a5502a4a70b8d796e62723f087c402.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇ <strong>Dorothy – Guild Receptionist</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > She charms adventurers with sweet words and cuteness, always getting them to do her bidding. But could there be a hidden agenda behind that smile…?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/extras/c73527c9950da912e9d5557b93a34845.avif?t=1774379683\" width=250 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "I arrived, full of spirit, only to find the dungeon already conquered?! While searching for clues to a new one, I ended up helping a village in crisis—gathering materials for every shop! How did I start getting close to all these unique and charming women?! What will become of my adventurer life?!", "supported_languages": "Traditional Chinese, English, Japanese<strong>*</strong>, Simplified Chinese, Korean<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/e29570cf235d61828953fcd3369105a20977f15e/header.jpg?t=1774379683", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/de95eed1d381c4fc7122b9a86890fa5c70b5ab8f/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1774379683", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3633750/de95eed1d381c4fc7122b9a86890fa5c70b5ab8f/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1774379683", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 560 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 4.3 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows7/8/10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 760 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 4.3 GB available space<br></li><li><strong>Sound Card:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026"}}}}, "fetched_at": "2026-04-22T04:59:31Z"}